    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Controller_Action_Helper_ContextSwitch class constructor takes one parameter; as the helper broker doesn't allow for constructor parameters when it instantiates helpers, it should be removed. The parameter is not used in the method body.</p>

